érale des étudiants et à leur permettre l'acquisition de connaissances spécifiques dans l'un ou l'autre des champs de l'histoire, de manière à pouvoir être facilement intégré à un projet global de formation universitaire au 1er cycle. Le programme est donc très souple pour mieux répondre aux besoins de formation très variés des étudiants inscrits à une majeure dans une autre discipline, ou à un baccalauréat facultaire pluridisciplinaire.","structure":"Version 07 (A16)\n\nLa mineure comporte 30 crédits.","segments":[{"id":"Segment 75","name":"","blocs":[{"id":"Bloc 75A","name":"Méthodologie et fondements","description":"Option - Minimum 9 crédits, maximum 24 crédits.","type":"Option","min":9.0,"max":24.0,"courses":["HST1010","HST1015","HST1031","HST1032","HST1041","HST1042","HST1043","HST1044","HST1051","HST1052","HST1053","HST1061","HST1062","HST1070","HST1080","HST2023","HST2101"]},{"id":"Bloc 75B","name":"Approfondissement","description":"Option - Minimum 3 crédits, maximum 18 crédits.","type":"Option","min":3.0,"max":18.0,"courses":["HST2070","HST2108","HST2109","HST2110","HST2111","HST2113","HST2125","HST2126","HST2128","HST2132","HST2139","HST2151","HST2212","HST2246","HST2262","HST2263","HST2264","HST2267","HST2273","HST2274","HST2276","HST2283","HST2288","HST2295","HST2296","HST2297","HST2298","HST2351","HST2352","HST2362","HST2370","HST2371","HST2401","HST2402","HST2410","HST2411","HST2420","HST2422","HST2427","HST2430","HST2443","HST2444","HST2446","HST2453","HST2621","HST2624","HST2625","HST2627","HST2628","HST2820","HST2831","HST2875","HST2885","HST2904","HST3133"]},{"id":"Bloc 75Z","name":"","description":"Choix - 3 crédits.\nSauf exception autorisée, les cours au choix doivent être choisis parmi les cours identifiés par un sigle autre que le sigle HST.","type":"Choix","min":3.0,"max":3.0,"courses":[]}],"description":"Les crédits de la mineure sont répartis de la façon suivante : 27 crédits à option et 3 crédits au choix."}],"courses":["HST1010","HST1015