udiciaire d'une plainte. Ils deviendront des experts et des leaders en matière de victimes, de victimisations, de victimes dans le système judiciaire et la justice internationale.","structure":"Version 01 (A23)\n\nLe D.E.S.S. comporte 30 crédits.","segments":[{"id":"Segment 70","name":"","blocs":[{"id":"Bloc 70A","name":"Méthodologie et outils d'analyse","description":"Option - Minimum 3 crédits, maximum 6 crédits.","type":"Option","min":3.0,"max":6.0,"courses":["CRI6001","CRI6002","CRI6003","CRI6220","DRT6500"]},{"id":"Bloc 70B","name":"Fondements","description":"Option - Minimum 6 crédits, maximum 9 crédits.","type":"Option","min":6.0,"max":9.0,"courses":["CRI6533","CRI6535","CRI6536"]},{"id":"Bloc 70C","name":"Cours de concentration","description":"Option - Minimum 12 crédits, maximum 18 crédits.","type":"Option","min":12.0,"max":18.0,"courses":["CRI6115","CRI6224","CRI6231","CRI6232","CRI6530","CRI6538","CRI6539","CRI6540","CRI6727","DRT6853"]},{"id":"Bloc 70D","name":"Connaissances complémentaires","description":"Option - Maximum 6 crédits.","type":"Option","min":0.0,"max":6.0,"courses":["CRI6006","CRI6007","CRI6008","CRI6010","CRI6112","CRI6114","CRI6118","CRI6119","CRI6121","CRI6221","CRI6226","CRI6228","CRI6229","CRI6233","CRI6234","CRI6532","CRI6534","CRI6702","CRI6720","CRI6721","CRI6722","CRI6723","CRI6725","CRI6726","CRI6730"]},{"id":"Bloc 70E","name":"","description":"Choix - Maximum 3 crédits.\nChoisir au maximum 3 crédits de cycles supérieurs dans le répertoire des cours de l'Université de Montréal ou toute autre université, avec l'approbation de la personne responsable du programme d'études suite à la recommandation du directeur de recherche.","type":"Choix","min":0.0,"max":3.0,"courses":[]}],"description":"Les crédits du D.E.S.S. sont répartis de la façon suivante : de 27 à 30 crédits à option, et de 0 à 3 crédits au choix."}],"courses":["CRI6001","CRI6002","CRI6003","CRI6220","DRT6500","CRI6533","CRI6535","CRI6536","CRI6115","CRI6224","CRI6231","CR