8)\n\nLa maîtrise comporte 45 crédits. L'étudiant doit choisir parmi les deux options suivantes:\n\n- Option Multidisciplinaire (segment 70)\n- Option Santé et sécurité au travail (segment 71)\n\nChaque option offre les modalités suivantes : \n- la modalité avec mémoire (MM),\n- la modalité avec stage (ST),\n- la modalité avec travail dirigé (TD).\n\nAux 45 crédits de la maîtrise peut s'ajouter une formation propédeutique composée des cours suivants :\nREI 6022 - 4 crédits - Politiques publiques et emploi  \nREI 6033 - 4 crédits - Aspects juridiques des RI  \nREI 6044 - 4 crédits - Gestion des ressources humaines  \nREI 6055 - 4 crédits - Relations du travail","segments":[{"id":"Segment 01","name":"Tronc commun","blocs":[{"id":"Bloc 01A","name":"","description":"Obligatoire - 6 crédits.","type":"Obligatoire","min":6.0,"max":6.0,"courses":["REI6600","REI6601"]}],"description":"Les crédits du tronc commun sont répartis de la façon suivante : 6 crédits obligatoires."},{"id":"Segment 70","name":"Propre à l'Option Multidisciplinaire","blocs":[{"id":"Bloc 70A","name":"","description":"Option - 9 crédits.","type":"Option","min":9.0,"max":9.0,"courses":["DRI6106","DRI6110","DRI6115","DRI6120","DRI6125","DRI6130","PLU6911A","REI6142","REI6143","REI6144","REI6170","REI6300","REI6604","REI6605","REI6606","REI6608","REI6610","REI6611","REI6613","REI6614","REI6615","REI6616","REI6617","REI6625","REI6626","REI6627","REI6628","REI6629","REI6630","REI6631","REI6632","SST6100","SST6200","SST6400"]},{"id":"Bloc 70B","name":"Recherche et mémoire","description":"Obligatoire - 30 crédits.","type":"Obligatoire","min":30.0,"max":30.0,"courses":["REI6905","REI6911","REI6920","REI6930"]},{"id":"Bloc 70A","name":"","description":"Option - Minimum 18 crédits, maximum 21 crédits.","type":"Option","min":18.0,"max":21.0,"courses":["DRI6106","DRI6110","DRI6115","DRI6120","DRI6125","DRI6130","PLU6911A","REI6142","REI6143","REI6144","REI6170","REI6300","REI6604","REI6605","REI6606","REI6608","REI66