ière en recherche de pointe dans les milieux universitaires, gouvernementaux ou industriels.</p>","structure":"Version 08 (H20)\n\nLe doctorat comporte 90 crédits. Il est offert en deux options:\n- option Biologie générale (segment 70)\n- option Muséologie (segment 71)","segments":[{"id":"Segment 70","name":"- Propre à l'option Biologie générale","blocs":[{"id":"Bloc 70A","name":"Cours de synthèse","description":"Option - Maximum 6 crédits.","type":"Option","min":0.0,"max":6.0,"courses":["BIO6028","BIO6034","BIO6035","BIO6036","BIO6037","BIO6106","BIO6115","BIO6157","BIO6204","BIO6205","BIO6206","BIO6250","BIO6260","BIO6390","BIO6432","BIO6441","BIO6756","BIO6790","BIO6822","BIO6851","BIO6866","BIO6872","BIO6875","BIO6965","BIO6970"]},{"id":"Bloc 70B","name":"Cours méthodologiques","description":"Option - Maximum 6 crédits.","type":"Option","min":0.0,"max":6.0,"courses":["BIO6004","BIO6020","BIO60321","BIO60322","BIO6033","BIO6065","BIO6077","BIO6245"]},{"id":"Bloc 70C","name":"Cours spécialisés","description":"Option - Maximum 6 crédits.","type":"Option","min":0.0,"max":6.0,"courses":["BIO6008","BIO7009","BIO7011"]},{"id":"Bloc 70D","name":"Cours connexes","description":"Option - Maximum 3 crédits.","type":"Option","min":0.0,"max":3.0,"courses":["BIN6002","EDD6050","ENV6002","MSL6515","NSC6060","NSC6070","TXL6014"]},{"id":"Bloc 70E","name":"","description":"Choix - Maximum 3 crédits.\nCours choisis avec l'approbation du responsable de programme.","type":"Choix","min":0.0,"max":3.0,"courses":[]},{"id":"Bloc 70F","name":"Recherche et thèse","description":"Obligatoire - 84 crédits.","type":"Obligatoire","min":84.0,"max":84.0,"courses":["BIO7000","BIO7001"]}],"description":"Les crédits de l'option sont répartis de la façon suivante : 84 crédits obligatoires attribués à la rédaction d'une thèse, de 3 à 6 crédits à option choisis parmi les cours des blocs 70A, 70B, 70C et un maximum de 3 crédits à option ou au choix parmi les cours des blocs 70D et 70E.\nLa répartition d